15:42.209 --> 15:46.513
- [panting]

15:46.546 --> 15:48.481
- DOCTOR SAID
YOU WERE DEHYDRATED,

15:48.515 --> 15:50.717
AND YOUR BLOOD PRESSURE
WAS REALLY HIGH.

15:50.750 --> 15:52.352
- HOW LONG
HAVE I BEEN HERE?

15:52.385 --> 15:54.554
- SINCE LAST NIGHT.

15:57.124 --> 15:58.758
