- I WAS WORRIED ABOUT YOU.

46:58.917 --> 47:00.085
- WELL, YOU COULD'VE CALLED.

47:00.118 --> 47:02.420
- I DID.
YOUR CELL PHONE WAS OFF.

47:02.453 --> 47:04.189
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

47:04.222 --> 47:06.524
- I'M REORGANIZING CDs.

47:06.557 --> 47:08.960
BEFORE THAT, I DID DVDs.

47:08.994 --> 47:11.629
I DID THE BOOKS,
I DID THE MEDICINE CABINET,

47:11.662 --> 47:14.332
I DID THE STEMWARE.
WHERE THE FUCK WERE YOU?

47:14.365 --> 47:16.601
- OUT.

47:16.634 --> 47:19.337
- WITH THE BOYS?
AT THE MOVIES?

47:19.370 --> 47:22.941
- I WAS WITH SOMEONE.

47:26.311 --> 47:28.079
THERE WAS THIS GUY
I DIDN'T TELL YOU ABOUT

47:28.113 --> 47:31.216
THAT I MET THE OTHER NIGHT
AT BABYLON.

47:31.249 --> 47:33.084
HE GAVE ME
HIS PHONE NUMBER.

